# --- Computer algebra & numerical computing --------------------------
# NOTE: SageMath is NOT shipped via apt on Trixie. The upstream Debian
# package was removed from testing/trixie due to RC bugs and a Python
# 3.12+ incompatibility (sagemath 9.5-6 depends on python3 < 3.12,
# while Trixie ships python3 3.13). The recommended path on AIMS OS
# v2.0 is `mamba install -c conda-forge sagemath` — we already ship
# Miniforge in aims-os-core for exactly this kind of edge case.
# Track the Debian RC bugs at https://tracker.debian.org/pkg/sagemath.
